 There was  a crack in the sky and a small pod landed. The bot already had a 
form so there was no reason for a scan. It was a warrior of old. He stepped 
out and looked across the land. He wa son Cybertron at this time he 
remembered. Waiting for news on Optimus Prime as the war waged on Cybertron. 
Thinking his brother was lost forever. Ultra Magnus transformed into his blue 
truck mode and sent out a comm to Hot Rod who's precense was always was felt 
in his spark like a sixth sense. He said "Hot Rod it is Magnus, I must speak 
with you I bring news."
